Novice Panel Missions

■Perform a limit break 3 times on a piece of first 5★ armor and enhance it to max
Strategy Tip:
• First 5★ armor are those with an initial rarity of 5★ and an initial CP of 35.
• They can be obtained by trading in five guard tokens at the guard token exchange.
　*The guard tokens needed to clear this mission can be obtained by clearing the mission "Clear Act 1, Ch. 1, 'Primus Island.'"
• The rewards for this mission are as follows.
Rewards
Guard Token×600
